name mp-gears
category Package
revision 78918
shortdesc Draw systems of intermeshing gears with MetaPost
longdesc This package helps to draw systems of intermeshing gears with
longdesc MetaPost. It allows users to model various gears/rack and
longdesc gear/rack systems (and even spirographs).
